The second cluster of CD3+ cells (Cluster 9), was a population of CD3D expressing cells with enriched expression of TBX21 (aka T-bet), KLRB1 (protein alias CD161), FCGR3A (CD16), NKG7, and GNLY (NKG5) with enriched expression of the TCR delta chain TRDC and the TCR gamma chain TRGC1. The expression profile of these cells suggests that the predominant population in this cluster may be unconventional γδ T cells
